com.i2group.apollo.commandservice.transport

Class AmendLink

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.i2group.apollo.commandservice.transport.Command
      • com.i2group.apollo.commandservice.transport.AmendLink
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICommand

    public final class AmendLink
extends Command
    The ICommand for amending a Link, rather than the Cards it contains.

    Leasing:

    • An active lease must exist on the Link to be amended.
    • The LinkType of the Link to be amended must not have ProhibitedEdit associated with it.
    Authorization:
    • The current user must have the SecurityAccessLevel.UPDATE access level for the Link.
    Validation:
    • The Link must not already be marked as deleted.
    • The ICommand must make at least one amendment. That is, at least one of getLinkDirection() and getLinkStrengthId() must return a non-null value.
    • If getLinkStrengthId() returns a non-null value, it must correspond to a LinkStrength in the Schema.
    Since:
    1.0
